commit.message:
Introduce new trie representation

Now each link to the next node stores also letter (an edge label),
thanks to that traversing the the trie is faster, as there are
fewer dereferences.

My tests show improvement up to 2 times, seems it's worth to do.

docs: move API overview to index.rst

README.rst has become too big and packed, full documentation
on readthedocs is way better.
Eliminate possible assertion error in save()

Fix handling memory error

Set next point might fail, it wasn't properly handled
and might have been source of (at least) memory leak.
